-## Social Teaser And Profile Cleanup
-
-- Created rollback archive:
-  `Docs/Design/SocialTeaserProfileArchive/2026-05-04-before-social-teaser-profile-cleanup/`.
-- Kept `SAVI` Release/TestFlight social-safe: Explore shows only `All` and
-  `Mine`, with a subtle `Friends are coming` Beta teaser instead of a real
-  Friends tab, add-friend input, public profile editing, or public publishing.
-- Kept `SAVI Test` Debug social-enabled for internal development: Friends scope,
-  friend actions, and the Social Beta profile card remain visible.
-- Reworked Release Profile into a cleaner stack: compact `SAVI Beta` card,
-  Backups, Private Vault, Appearance, Guide, Account/iCloud, Library tools, and
-  a small `Coming soon` Social Beta note.
-- Softened the disabled social sheet copy to explain that Social is coming
-  rather than presenting a broken feature.
-- Built and installed both simulator channels:
-  `com.savi.app` and `com.altatecrd.savi.personaldebug`.
-- Captured QA screenshots:
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_social_teaser_explore_release_2026-05-04.jpg`,
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_social_teaser_explore_footer_release_2026-05-04.jpg`,
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_profile_cleanup_release_2026-05-04.jpg`,
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_test_social_explore_debug_2026-05-04.jpg`,
-  and
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_test_social_profile_debug_2026-05-04.jpg`.
